Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:08.36,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Once there was a man who obtained everything,\Nthe legendary Pirate King Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:12.91,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,His last words before he was executed inspired people to sail the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.91,0:00:14.63,Gold,Roger,0,0,0,,All my wealth and treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:16.27,Gold,Roger,0,0,0,,It can be yours if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:17.42,Gold,Roger,0,0,0,,Search for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.42,0:00:19.79,Gold,Roger,0,0,0,,I left everything in that one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:22.82,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,People now set sail in search of romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.82,0:00:25.40,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The world has entered a Great Age of Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.62,0:02:33.97,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,T-The Noah is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.46,0:02:44.06,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,The Noah isn't crashing into us anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:48.56,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,The Princess is luring the boat away for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:50.52,Main,Citizen2,0,0,0,,Princess Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:52.20,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Please make it out alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.53,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,Where do you think you're going, Shirahoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:03:00.44,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,There's no place you can run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:04.37,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:14.34,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,I have to make it out into the sea\Nand pull the Noah off the bubble!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:26.07,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,It'll be awful if the bubble is damaged more than it has been already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.48,0:03:29.91,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,But it's too far to make it to the main gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:38.08,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama's friends must have been\Nthe last people to leave Ryuuguu Palace...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:42.45,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)}so maybe they left the connecting channel open!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:51.25,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Damn it, isn't there anything we can do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:56.19,Main,Fishman2,0,0,0,,The Princess is risking her life to save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.19,0:04:00.00,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,It isn't the Princess' fault\Nthat Decken has been stalking her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:03.20,Main,Fishman2,0,0,0,,Decken's on board that boat.  And it's not just him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:05.47,Main,Fishman2,0,0,0,,Hody is also climbing aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:08.51,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Princess Shirahoshi's life is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:12.24,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,That insane backstabbing Decken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:17.15,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,But I've still got a use for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:20.62,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,Watch out for Hody, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:26.46,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,In the water, humans are no match for fishmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.13,0:04:28.67,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.67,0:04:33.67,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,It won't be any good if I break the outside bubble\Nand send him into the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:38.10,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,I've gotta get it just right.\NIt can't be too strong nor too weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:38.97,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:07.00,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,This sure is a huge chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:10.31,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,So this is between the two bubble layers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:14.90,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.90,0:05:16.94,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,He's still below the first bubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:24.12,Main,Fishmen,0,0,0,,Pull!  Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:28.99,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,We can't stop it, but maybe we can\Nslow it down a tiny bit for the Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:31.89,Main,Fishman(offscreen),0,0,0,,A tiny bit might be enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:33.39,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:35.56,Main,Fishman2,0,0,0,,Stop the Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:40.47,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Princess!  Please use this chance to find a safe place!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:46.68,Main,Fishman2,0,0,0,,Dammit!  Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:48.64,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,The merfolk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:50.18,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:56.41,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,Are you guys for real?!\NThere's no way it'll move a single inch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:58.61,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,Wasting your energy like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:00.82,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey!  Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:06.73,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,You little pieces of filth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.73,0:06:12.84,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,Humans underestimate fishmankind because of cowards like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:17.51,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.51,0:06:19.40,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:23.48,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Princess... run away... quickly... please...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:25.12,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,As I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.12,0:06:27.98,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,The entrance to Ryuuguu Palace was left open!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:30.40,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Don't die on me, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:32.03,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Damn you Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.98,0:06:35.40,Main,Fishman2,0,0,0,,Princess Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:39.19,Main,Fishman2,0,0,0,,She used the connecting channel to get into the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:42.92,Main,Fishman2,0,0,0,,The Noah's following her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:44.95,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Princess!  Please keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:51.59,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Whoa!  It's goin' up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:03.62,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Wait up, chain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:06.97,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,You act all high and mighty on land...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:11.91,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,but in the sea, you couldn't even put up a decent fight\Nagainst a fishman child!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.09,0:07:15.85,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,This really is the limit of human strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:20.25,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,I'll make you regret ever opposing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:26.73,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:31.14,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,You enjoying your freedom?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:36.23,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,The walls of Koukaku Tower kept you safe\Nfor ten years, but they can't help you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.94,0:07:40.36,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,Will you die from blood loss?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:45.30,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,Or will you be smashed by this behemoth first?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:49.58,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,I'll give you one last chance, Shirahoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.58,0:07:54.51,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,Say {\i1}yes{\i0}, and I'll spare your life.  It's still not too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:57.63,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry, Decken-sama, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.63,0:07:59.88,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,Marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:01.08,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,...you're just not my{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:03.27,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,Well then, die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:09.39,Main,Manboshi,0,0,0,,You think we'd let you marry her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:15.01,Main,Manboshi,0,0,0,,We won't let you put a single finger on our only sister, Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:19.02,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,My dearest brothers,\NManboshi-sama and Ryuuboshi-sama!  And Hoe-sama!{ def: double check for three lines in workraw-sd }
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:23.30,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,Wha?!  Our brothers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:24.68,Main,Ryuuboshi+Manboshi,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're not your brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:35.04,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Dearest brothers, everyone in the plaza tried to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:37.41,Main,Manboshi,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi!  Save the crying for later!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:39.97,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,My dearest brothers are angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:43.16,Main,Manboshi,0,0,0,,We're not angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:48.58,Main,Ryuuboshi,0,0,0,,Father said that the Noah is an important ship,\Nso we can't allow it to get a single scratch -la-ti-do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:53.84,Main,Ryuuboshi,0,0,0,,That means we have to return it\Nto the sea floor without damaging it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:55.58,Main,Manboshi,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:09:02.62,Main,Manboshi,0,0,0,,Damn it!  In any case, we can't swim near the underwater mountains or ravines.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:04.41,Main,Manboshi,0,0,0,,That would damage the Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:07.71,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,So where should I escape to, dearest Manboshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:12.52,Main,Manboshi,0,0,0,,Up!  There are too many obstacles on the sea floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:14.62,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:17.65,Main,Ryuuboshi,0,0,0,,We'll get Decken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:36.05,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,From the Noah... and my endless love...\Nyou will never be able to escape, Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:46.50,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey, thanks!  You saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:48.73,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Does the wound that you got from Hody\Nstill bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:52.43,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,I won't let you get away, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:59.00,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,I don't have time to worry about a wound like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:07.80,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,You may be a member of the merman race, who pride themselves on being the world's fastest swimmers...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:10.36,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,but compared to me, it's like you're not even moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:11.29,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,That guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.49,0:10:16.03,Note,Hody,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Shark cutter
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:32.49,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey, get me onto the ship's deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:35.89,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,It's like Jinbe said...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:38.66,Flashbacks,Luffy,0,0,0,,Do you think there's water inside the ship, Jinbe? { from 558 }
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.66,0:10:43.23,Flashbacks,Jinbe,0,0,0,,I'm not sure, but Decken is a Devil Fruit user...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:46.44,Flashbacks,Jinbe,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)}so we can assume that there must be air in there somewhere since he can make the ship move. { end 558 }
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:49.10,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,So it should be easier to fight in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:53.55,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I want to defeat both Hody and\Nthat guy who keeps throwing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.55,0:10:58.03,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I promised Weak-hoshi that I would protect her\Nwhen I took her out of the tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:11:00.71,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,A promise, you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.25,0:11:05.32,Flashbacks,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,We'll become great soldiers like our father. {21:07.03 in ep 546}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.19,0:11:13.05,Flashbacks,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)}Just as we promised,\Nwe'll protect Shirahoshi with our lives! { end 546 }
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:15.67,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,We've made a promise too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:19.92,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,His strength is nothing more than a mockery, borrowed from the Energy Steroids.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:23.26,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,It's pitiful to think that\NI couldn't stand up to that rogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:27.10,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,Forgive us for doubting you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:29.52,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.  Just get me onto the deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:31.40,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,Is there something you want on the deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:33.69,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.09,0:11:36.10,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Up, up...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.92,0:11:46.90,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,Oh, Hody Jones.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:51.51,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,How's Neptune?  Did you kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:55.93,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,I'm just in the middle\Nof tormenting Shirahoshi with the Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.93,0:11:58.48,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,Wasn't this a great idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:00.68,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,Don't you think so, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.48,0:12:06.62,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,I also have a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.34,0:12:13.28,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,What is it?  Will you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:16.98,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,If you die...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:35.81,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,...what will happen to this boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:45.23,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,Decken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:08.97,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,Hody... You little brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:14.66,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,I just touched you... with my left hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:19.20,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,Now, tell me what the hell you think you're doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:24.83,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,You betrayed me first, Decken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:31.76,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,Honestly, I panicked for a second\Nwhen this ship blocked the sky above the island. { def: it really isn't sky... but it really isn't an island either }
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:36.44,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,Breaking the island's bubble is a good idea, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:41.24,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,True, Fishman Island will crumble with it, but the Fishman District will remain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:47.21,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,If you die here and now,\Nyour Mato Mato powers will stop working...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.21,0:13:52.32,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,and the ship will plunge straight down toward Fishman Island once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:58.20,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,It will annihilate everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:14:04.83,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,Right now, my top priority\Nis destroying those pesky Straw Hat Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.83,0:14:08.25,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,Tens of thousands of my own men may die as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:13.63,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,Oh well, I can always get more human slaves later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:20.18,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,You want everyone to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:23.41,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,That sounds good...
